snippet.title: Context Free
snippet.description:
Context Free is about programming languages, including design, usage, implementation, and history.

As for me, my name is Tom. I started programming in Basic as a kid in the 80s. I find both computer and human languages super fun. While I'm a professional programmer, languages is a hobby for me. In addition to using programming languages, I also dabble in programming language design and development. I hope this channel is useful to folks out there!

https://contextfree.info/
https://twitter.com/contextfreeinfo
https://reddit.com/r/contextfree/
https://github.com/contextfreecode
https://tjpalmer.github.io/languish/
https://github.com/tjpalmer/rio
